sdl:
schema  { query: QueryRoot }

type ArticleAggregate { avg: ArticleAggregateAvg
  count: ArticleAggregateCount
  nodes: [ArticleFields!]!
  sum: ArticleAggregateSum
}

type ArticleAggregateAvg { authorId: Int
  id: Int
}

type ArticleAggregateCount { authorId: Int!
  content: Int!
  id: Int!
  title: Int!
}

type ArticleAggregateSum { authorId: Int
  id: Int
}

type ArticleFields { authorId: Int
  content: String
  id: Int
  title: String
}

type ArticleGroup { groupAggregate: ArticleAggregate!
  groupKey: ArticleFields!
}

type AuthorAggregate { avg: AuthorAggregateAvg
  count: AuthorAggregateCount
  nodes: [AuthorFields!]!
  sum: AuthorAggregateSum
}

type AuthorAggregateAvg { id: Int
}

type AuthorAggregateCount { id: Int!
  name: Int!
}

type AuthorAggregateSum { id: Int
}

type AuthorFields { id: Int
  name: String
}

type AuthorGroup { groupAggregate: AuthorAggregate!
  groupKey: AuthorFields!
}

type QueryRoot { articleAggregate(where: ArticleBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): ArticleAggregate!
  articleFindOneById: ArticleFields
  articleGroup(groupBy: [ArticleField!], where: ArticleBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): [ArticleGroup!]!
  articleList(where: ArticleBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): [ArticleFields!]!
  authorAggregate(where: AuthorBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): AuthorAggregate!
  authorFindOneById: AuthorFields
  authorGroup(groupBy: [AuthorField!], where: AuthorBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): [AuthorGroup!]!
  authorList(where: AuthorBooleanExpression, limit: Int, offset: Int): [AuthorFields!]!
}

enum ArticleField {AuthorId 
  Content 
  Id 
  Title 
}

enum AuthorField {Id 
  Name 
}

input ArticleBooleanExpression {and: [ArticleBooleanExpression!]
  authorId: IntComparisonExpression
  content: StringComparisonExpression
  id: IntComparisonExpression
  not: ArticleBooleanExpression
  or: [ArticleBooleanExpression!]
  title: StringComparisonExpression
}

input AuthorBooleanExpression {and: [AuthorBooleanExpression!]
  id: IntComparisonExpression
  name: StringComparisonExpression
  not: AuthorBooleanExpression
  or: [AuthorBooleanExpression!]
}

input IntComparisonExpression {eq: Int
}

input StringComparisonExpression {eq: String
}
